{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_04_03",
  "title": "LizNoir 04 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirは世間の予想通り、順当に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――As the world expected‚ LizNoir steadily",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリを勝ち進んでいった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "continued to rack up victories in the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7400000890096026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 7.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "さ、食べなさい\nお腹空いたでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ eat up.\nYou must be hungry‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……これ、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What’s this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.7666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.299637095133464
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたって……\n私達の夕食よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean‚ “What’s this?”…\nIt’s our dinner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.76630376180013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.799637095133463
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "まさかとは思うけど\n莉央が作ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to assume‚ but…\nDid you make this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.66630376180013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ\n私、キッチンにいたでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nI was in the kitchen‚ wasn’t I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.46630376180013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.566303761800132
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央が夕食に誘ったくせに部屋に連れてくるから\n僕てっきりピザでも頼むのかと思ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You invited me to dinner and then brought me to your room‚\nso I naturally thought we were going to order pizza or something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.066303761800132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.26630376180013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私は基本的には自炊よ\n……スイーツ以外は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I usually cook for myself.\n…Except for sweets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.09963709513346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.96630376180012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央って料理出来たんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know how to cook.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.96630376180012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.332970428466794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "前から思ってたんだけど\n貴方、無自覚に失礼よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been thinking this for a while‚ but…\nYou’re unconsciously rude‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.59963709513346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.832970428466794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "いただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Itadakimasu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.832970428466794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.16630376180012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、美味しい\n莉央、料理上手なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ it’s good.\nYou’re a good cook‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.46630376180012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.16630376180012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "家が喫茶店をやってたから\n軽食も出していたしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My family runs a cafe‚\nso we also serve light meals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.832970428466794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.832970428466794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ていうか、私が料理するのそんなに変？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ is it that strange that I cook?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8329704284668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.817346858978276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "僕、莉央は歌と踊りとパンケーキの\n毎日だと思っていたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always thought all you did every day was sing‚ dance‚\nand eat pancakes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.450680192311616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.08401352564495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "本当に失礼な子ね\nおかわりは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re such a rude child.\nWant more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.05068019231162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.58401352564495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、いただくよ\nこんなに美味しいご飯は久しぶりだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I’ll have more.\nThis is the first delicious meal I’ve had in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.28401352564494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.61734685897827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、葵は実家暮らしなのよね\nお母さんがご飯を作ってくれるんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ you live at home with your family‚ don’t you?\nYour mother cooks for you‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.11734685897827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.8506801923116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろだよ\nお母さんが作る時もあるけど兄貴が作ることも多いよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It depends.\nMy mother cooks sometimes‚ but my older brother cooks a lot too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.15068019231161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.38401352564495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "お兄さんがいたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have an older brother?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.38401352564495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、弟もね\n僕はまん中で唯一の女なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I have a younger brother too.\nI’m the only girl in the middle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1506801923116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.1506801923116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "両親は忙しいから\n兄貴が炊事洗濯をやったりするんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My parents are busy‚\nso my brother does the cooking and laundry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.81734685897824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "男兄弟だと食事は質より量なんだよ\n僕が担当の時はカレーかシチューって決まってるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With brothers‚ it’s more about quantity than quality when it comes to meals.\nWhen it’s my turn to cook‚ it’s always curry or stew.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.45068019231148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.88401352564482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "貴方、女の子がそれじゃダメよ\nいいわ、グランプリが終わったら料理を教えてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can’t be like that as a girl‚ Aoi.\nAlright‚ I’ll teach you how to cook after the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4840135256449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
